{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_09_02",
  "title": "鈴村優 2話 客観的な意見が必要なはずや",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "まさか瑠依ちゃんにだけ\n特番のオファーがきとったなんてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was unexpected that only Rui-chan\nreceived the offer for the special program…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "しかも番組のアシスタントMCやなんて、大役やん\n受ければ、大きなキャリアになること間違いなしや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Furthermore‚ it’s the assistant MC for the program‚ that’s a big role!\nIf she accepts‚ it’ll definitely be a great addition to her career.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、瑠依一人じゃ決められない問題だからな\nまずは、トリエルの三人で話し合うよう伝えたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ this is not something Rui can decide on her own.\nI told her to first discuss it with the other members in TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依も、悩んでいる様子ではなかったが\nまだ話していないところを見ると……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui didn’t seem troubled‚\nbut seeing as she hasn’t talked about it yet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.8695921302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "大きな決断になるし、自分なりに考えをまとめてから\n二人に話したかったのかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a big decision‚ so maybe she wanted to\norganize her thoughts before talking to the other two.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "考えを整理してから、っていうことやんな\n真面目な瑠依ちゃんらしいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So she is clearing her mind‚ before talking about that.\nSounds just like diligent Rui-chan~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみにこのオファーについて、優はどう思う？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ what do you think about this offer‚ Yu?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.5254191239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "せやなぁ\n瑠依ちゃんの気持ちは本人から聞くとして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well~.\nI’ll hear Rui’s thoughts from her directly… but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "うちとしては、またとない機会やし\n特番の方に出た方がいいと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As for me‚ she should appear on the special program\nsince it’s a very rare opportunity.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.9420063018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "その方が、瑠依ちゃんの今後のためにも\nトリエルの今後のためにもなるはずや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’ll be good for Rui’s future‚\nand for the future of TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "今後か。先方は、この特番を今年だけじゃなく\n毎年恒例の一大イベントにしたいそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The future… They want to make this special program\na major annual event‚ not just a one-time thing this year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "来年にも繋がるんなら、なおさらや\nトリエルは、もっと高みに上らなあかん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it continues next year‚ that’s all the more reason.\nTRINITYAiLE needs to aim higher.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "それに、うちらが頂点に立つ姿を見せることこそが\nお世話になってきた人達への恩返しにもなるはずや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ showing everyone who has helped us\nthat we’ve reached the top will also show our gratitude.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "最終回には、うちとすみれちゃんで出ます\n瑠依ちゃんは、特番の方に出演させてあげて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan and I will appear on the final episode.\nLet Rui-chan appear on the special program.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依のことと、グループの今後を考えた\n優らしい選択だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a very Yu-like decision‚\nthinking about Rui and the future of the group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "これが最善の選択やと思います。ほな、三人での\n話し合いに向けて、うちも考えをまとめとかんとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think this is the best choice. Then‚ I should\norganize my thoughts before we discuss it as a group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "話すのはうちの得意分野やし、期待してて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Talking is my specialty‚ so you can count on me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.9623346647,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3055776597,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1314.9426898999934,
          "startTime": 117.6205203496
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.3055776597
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.3055776597
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、おはようございます～\n今日のスケジュールなんやけど――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san‚ good morning.\nAbout today’s schedule――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.1513391179
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "――って、なんで下ばっか見てるん？\nこんな可愛い子が目の前におるのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Hey‚ why are you just looking down?\nHere’s such a cute girl in front of you~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いや、そういうファッションだったら悪いんだが……\n優、靴下が左右で違うみたいだぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I'm sorry if that's your fassion style on purpose… but…\nYu‚ your socks don’t match.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.6624958993
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　あ……ほんまや。全然気付かんかった\nうちったらうっかりさんやな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? Ah… you’re right. I didn’t notice at all~.\nI’m such an airhead~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……優らしくないな\n何かあったんじゃないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That’s unlike you.\nDid something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.9953077
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さんっていつもは鈍感やのに\nこういう時は気付きはるんやね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san‚ you’re usually so oblivious‚\nbut you’re so perceptive at times like this~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "……この前、特番うんぬんの話があったやろ？\nそれについてトリエルの三人で話し合ったんやけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You remember we talked about that special program the other day?\nThe three of us in TRINITYAiLE talked about that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.6902538522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.7294193269
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "揉めに揉めて、答えを出すんは、一旦保留になりました\n得意分野とか言ったのに、恥ずかしいわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But after we argued back and forth‚ we put off coming to a conclusion for now.\nI said it was my specialty and all‚ I’m so embarrassed~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.1333180745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、瑠依に反対されたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be that Rui opposed it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.3999865216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.8159955821
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
